<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <xsl:apply-templates select="//ProjectStageHistory"/> </ROOT> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="ProjectStageHistory"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:copy-of select = "@*"/>
<xsl:if test="string(@DateFirstEntered) and not(string(@DateLastEntered))"> <xsl:attribute name="DateLastEntered"> <xsl:value-of select="@DateFirstEntered"/> </xsl:attribute> </xsl:if>
<xsl:if test="string(@DateFirstFinished) and not(string(@DateLastFinished))"> <xsl:attribute name="DateLastFinished"> <xsl:value-of select="@DateFirstFinished"/> </xsl:attribute> </xsl:if>

<xsl:if test="string(@DateFirstEntered) and (string(@DateLastFinished) or string(@DateFirstFinished))"> <xsl:attribute name="TotalDuration"> <xsl:value-of select="AS:NormalRound(AS:DifferenceInMinutes(@DateFirstEntered, AS:isnull(@DateLastFinished, @DateFirstFinished)) div 1440, 2)"/> </xsl:attribute> </xsl:if>
<xsl:if test="string(@DateLastEntered) and string(@DateLastFinished)"> <xsl:attribute name="LastDuration"> <xsl:value-of select="AS:NormalRound(AS:DifferenceInMinutes(@DateLastEntered, @DateLastFinished) div 1440, 2)"/> </xsl:attribute> </xsl:if>
<xsl:copy-of select = "*"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template>
</xsl:stylesheet>

SchemaItem.Name: Generate_ProjectTaskTimesheetHeader
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">
<xsl:param name="parDateFrom"/> <xsl:param name="parDateTo"/> <xsl:param name="parResourceId"/>
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <xsl:apply-templates select="ProjectTask"/> <xsl:call-template name="GeneratePTTH"/> </ROOT> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="ProjectTask"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:copy-of select="@*"/> <xsl:copy-of select="*[name() != 'ProjectTaskTimesheet']"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template name="GeneratePTTH"> <xsl:param name="Date" select="$parDateFrom"/>
<xsl:if test="AS:DifferenceInDays($Date, $parDateTo) >= 0"> <ProjectTaskTimesheetHeader Id="{AS:GenerateId()}" Date="{substring-before($Date,'T')}" refResourceId="{$parResourceId}"> <xsl:for-each select="/ROOT/ProjectTask"> <xsl:choose> <!--if there is no timesheet generate 1 new record--> <xsl:when test="count(ProjectTaskTimesheet[substring-before(@Date,'T')=substring-before($Date,'T')]/@Id)=0"> <ProjectTaskTimesheet Id="{AS:GenerateId()}" Date="{substring-before($Date,'T')}" refProjectId="{@refProjectId}" refProjectTaskId="{@Id}" refResourceId="{$parResourceId}" /> </xsl:when> <!--if there is timesheet already generate new records that equals to timesheet amount--> <xsl:otherwise><xsl:copy-of select="ProjectTaskTimesheet[substring-before(@Date,'T')=substring-before($Date,'T')]"/></xsl:otherwise> </xsl:choose> </xsl:for-each>
<xsl:for-each select="/ROOT/ProjectTaskTimesheet_NoTask[substring-before(@Date,'T')=substring-before($Date,'T')]"> <ProjectTaskTimesheet> <xsl:copy-of select="@*"/> <xsl:copy-of select="*"/> </ProjectTaskTimesheet> </xsl:for-each>
</ProjectTaskTimesheetHeader> <xsl:call-template name="GeneratePTTH"><xsl:with-param name="Date" select="AS:AddDays($Date, '1')"/></xsl:call-template> </xsl:if> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>
